| Failure                  | Mitigation                                             |
| ------------------------ | ------------------------------------------------------ |
| Archival fails midway    | Use Durable Functions checkpoints to resume            |
| Blob read latency        | Cache popular records or use Azure CDN                 |
| Cosmos DB query timeouts | Use continuation tokens for pagination                 |
| Blob record not found    | Return 404, log anomaly                                |
| High load on read shim   | Auto-scale API layer or use Azure API Management cache |
